description:
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking individuals with excellent organisational skills, a range of computer skills and experience in working as a secretary. Good communication and interpersonal skills, a friendly approach, enthusiasm and motivation are all required for this post. Previous experience of working within a medical secretary environment is desirable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The position will primarily be based in the Gastroenterology department, although cover in other areas of the Speciality Admin Team may be required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The working pattern will be agreed on successful appointment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We require the candidates to have skills in all areas of administrative functions to enable them to support the patient pathway, using Standard Operating Procedures (SOP’s) to ensure that functions of the role are carried out correctly within given timescales.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dawn Blakey, Team Leader&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;03033 302801&lt;/p&gt;
